a.What is the use of SQLitel Open helper class in SQLite?
ans.SQLite open helper class provide the functionality to use the SQLite 
Database for storing data in Android Application.It helps to open and create 
database using OnCreate and OnUpgrade method and do the CRUD operation.

b.What is the use of OnUpgrade function in SQLiteOpenHelper class?
ans.OnUpgade methods helps to maintain the database version.It usually calls in 
the application when database schema has changed for ex.Table defiation has 
chaged or some constrained has added to the database.

c.How to show SQLite database table information in android application what is 
the best way to do it?

ans.We can show the table information using table layout with cursor in android application.